{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-post-template-tsx","path":"/posts/newsupdates_vpn_data_breach/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"80792260-7ae1-5e09-b6d7-414ac700de08","html":"<p><img src=\"/media/vpn_hacked_cover.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"事發經過\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BA%8B%E7%99%BC%E7%B6%93%E9%81%8E\" aria-label=\"事發經過 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>事發經過</h2>\n<h3 id=\"外洩原因\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%A4%96%E6%B4%A9%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0\" aria-label=\"外洩原因 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>外洩原因</h3>\n<p>市面上七款 VPN 大量搜集用戶個人資料，並存放於公開且未加密的 Elasticsearch Server 資料庫中，任何人都可以讀取資料庫內的所有資訊</p>\n<h3 id=\"外洩資料\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%A4%96%E6%B4%A9%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99\" aria-label=\"外洩資料 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>外洩資料</h3>\n<p>活動紀錄、個資、密碼、比特幣付款資訊、個人裝置資訊、帳號資訊、Paypal 資訊、用戶 IP 位置</p>\n<h3 id=\"外洩資料量\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%A4%96%E6%B4%A9%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E9%87%8F\" aria-label=\"外洩資料量 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>外洩資料量</h3>\n<p>1.207 TB，影響超過 2000 萬用戶</p>\n<h3 id=\"受影響的-vpn\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%97%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%9A%84-vpn\" aria-label=\"受影響的 vpn permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>受影響的 VPN</h3>\n<p>UFO VPN、FAST VPN、Free VPN、Super VPN、Flash VPN、Secure VPN、Rabbit VPN</p>\n<h2 id=\"供應商的回應-20200715\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E5%95%86%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-20200715\" aria-label=\"供應商的回應 20200715 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>供應商的回應 (2020/07/15)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>收到洩漏通知後 10 天才加密、保護資料庫</li>\n<li>宣稱搜集的皆為匿名後資訊</li>\n<li>否認外洩資料包含使用者資訊和密碼</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"回應遭打臉\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E9%81%AD%E6%89%93%E8%87%89\" aria-label=\"回應遭打臉 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>回應遭打臉</h2>\n<p>外洩截圖遭揭露者公佈，證實外洩內容包含使用者個資和密碼</p>\n<h2 id=\"用戶該怎麼應對\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E8%A9%B2%E6%80%8E%E9%BA%BC%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D\" aria-label=\"用戶該怎麼應對 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>用戶該怎麼應對？</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>停止使用這些 VPN，改為使用可信任開發商之產品</li>\n<li>個資外洩可能造成使用者成為首要攻擊目標，接下來必須多防範釣魚或詐騙的狀況</li>\n<li>遭外洩之 Paypal 用戶除了更改密碼，更要注意盜刷或盜用的狀況</li>\n<li>將使用相同帳密的其他服務都更改密碼</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"資料來源\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90\" aria-label=\"資料來源 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>資料來源</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.vpnmentor.com/blog/report-free-vpns-leak/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">vpnMentor - Report: No-Log VPNs Exposed Users’ Logs and Personal Details for All to See</a></p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/2020-07-21-news-updates-7款免費vpn大量用戶個資外洩//posts/newsupdates_vpn_data_breach","tagSlugs":["/tag/vpn/","/tag/data-breach/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-07-21T00:00:27.850Z","description":"市面上七款免費VPN因資料外洩遭踢爆大量搜集用戶個資，總資料外洩量1.207 TB，超過2000萬用戶受到影響。","tags":["VPN","data breach"],"title":"7款免費VPN 外洩大量用戶個資","socialImage":"/media/vpn_hacked_cover.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/2020-07-21-news-updates-7款免費vpn大量用戶個資外洩//posts/newsupdates_vpn_data_breach"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2246977889","2727970573","911332639"],"slicesMap":{}}